–34
</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[299,328,535,560]" captionStart="FIGURES 56 – 59" captionStartId="23.[151,264,1683,1706]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1661]" captionTargetId="figure@23.[151,1436,193,1662]" captionTargetPageId="23" captionText="FIGURES 56 – 59. Stethantyx spp., ♀, holotypes, habitus: 56 — S. neopropodeator sp. nov.; 57 — S. orellana sp. nov.; 58 — S. sinuata sp. nov.; 59 — S. tiputinia sp. nov. Scales 1.0 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/248197/files/figure.png" pageId="14" pageNumber="315">57</figureCitation>
